10th Floor, Gokuldas Tejpal Hospital Complex Building,
Read: Letter from Health Services Commissionerate, Mumbai No. By / Room-3 / T-2 / No.2401
bela, T. 30-bed rural primary health centre at Umred, District Nagpur
A proposal to upgrade the hospital was under the consideration of the government.
bela, T. The Government is approving the upgradation of Primary Health Centre at Umred, District Nagpur to a 30-bed rural hospital as a "special case."
By acquiring a site in the prescribed manner for a 30-bed rural hospital in this upgraded category.
Construction and post-production will be dealt with separately.
This Government decision is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
